site_name: Blocks E and C, Phase 5, Kidbrooke Masterplan, Kidbrooke Park Road, Kidbrooke, SE3
description: An application submitted under Section 96a of the Town & Country Planning Act 1990 for a non material amendment in connection with the planning permission dated 27/03/2015 (Reference: 14/2611/F) for the demolition of existing buildings and construction of 1,144 residential units (an increase of 258 residential units over and above the 2013 consent figure of 886 dwellings), publicly accessible open space and associated access, car parking, cycle parking and landscaping as varied by Section 73 application dated 26/01/2016 (Reference: 15/2862/MA) to allow:- Amendment to the approved accommodation schedule and approved affordable housing plan (as listed within condition 1) to relocate the shared ownership and private units within Phase 5 of the Kidbrooke Village redevelopment (Block C and E only).
